Through this partnership, ITTS aims not only to enhance research and education in the field of information security but also to open wider opportunities for internship programs, applied research collaborations, and capacity development for students and lecturers in collaboration with industry professionals. We firmly believe that synergy between academia and industry is the key to nurturing digital talents who are well-prepared to face real-world challenges, particularly in the areas of information security and national digital transformation.
